            <span>90%</span>
            <p>of conference attendees donâ€™t know which of their LinkedIn connections will also be there</p>
        </li>
        <li class="text">
            <span>33%</span>
            <p>of conference attendees focus more than half of their time on re-connecting with previous friends/connections</p>
